run ./chromedriver to determine what version is currently installed (it is 2.32 as of this writing)

go here to see what browser versions this version of the driver supports:
http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/2.32/notes.txt

you can see what version of chrome is running on bamboo by running:
google-chrome --version

you should be able to upgrade bamboo with:
sudo apt-get install google-chrome-stable

all versions of chromedriver are available here:
https://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html